features: 【Designed for Small Spaces】This small side table has a slim figure of 15.4"L x 11.4"W x 20"H, which fits perfectly in most small spaces, putting in the living room as a sofa table or as a bed side table in the bedroom. It's all up to you!

【 Industrial Style】Retro-colored panels reflect a sense of time. The black metal frame adds not only sturdiness but also better weight bearing. The perfect combination of retro and industrial style makes small side table perfect for integrating into any home decor.
【Sturdy and Durable】Made of premium particleboard and strong metal frame, this small end table is solid and stable for long-term use, capable of holding 44lb of items on each tier.

【Protect your Floor】We provide 4 adjustable feet for you to adjust the small end table on uneven floors. The plastic feet also prevent the metal legs from directly touching the floor to avoid scratches.
【Assembly is a Breeze】Clear and detailed instructions, and numbered parts are all included in the package, allowing you assemble the small side table for small spaces quickly and esaily in minutes.
body.description: Tajsoon 2-Tier Small Side Table Making every inch of space to decorate and organize your home is essential. This two-tiered side table can be placed next to a sofa, next to a bed, on a balcony, or next to a lounge chair. This small end table is made of black steel tubing, smooth wood and a rustic brown finish. It is the perfect match for any home decor. The two-tier flat design allows for the placement of items and storage needs. It will organize and enhance the whole home well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars nice little small end table
reviews.reviewText: First when i opened the box and looked at the instructions i was surprised there we no written instructions just drawings of the pieces and what goes where. These were easy to follow since there is very few parts to this table and all the screws were clearly marked in the bags and even included the necessary allen wrench to put together. Overall quality is good and nice looking serves my purpose just fine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Needed small table for small space
reviews.reviewText: Used this as bedside table. Fit perfectly in the space I had to work with. The 3 shelves give me enough space for item storage. Easy to put together. Took me less than an hour. Table is sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Looks great in our guest room! It is a little wobbly but we were able to fix it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: My husband put this adorable table together very quickly and said it was very sturdy. He’s an aeronautical engineer and follows instructions to a tee! It took maybe 15 minutes to set up. Perfect size to go between two chairs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Great little table for the money. Perfect for small area. Easy assembly/directions. There were 3packages of screws. The table required 4 screws in each package. They provided an extra screw in each package along with the required Allen wrench.. Relatively sturdy. Would definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Side Table with Adjustable Screw - 4 Stars
reviews.reviewText: **Pros:*** Easy assembly* All parts labeled clearly* Extra screws included* Tool included* Adjustable screw on the bottom for uneven surfaces* Perfect height for my needs* Feels sturdy and stable**Cons:*** Black finish on the top shelf was damaged on one corner**Overall:**I am generally happy with this side table. The assembly was easy, the parts were labeled clearly, and there were even extra screws and a tool included. I love the adjustable screw on the bottom, which allows me to use the table on uneven surfaces. The height is perfect for my needs, and the table feels sturdy and stable. My only complaint is that the black finish on the top shelf was damaged on one corner. However, this is a minor issue, and I am still happy with the table overall**Recommendation:**I would recommend this side table to others. It is a well-made, sturdy table that is easy to assemble. The adjustable screw is a great feature, and the height is perfect for many different uses. The only downside is the minor damage to the black finish, but this is not a major issue.
